channel.title: Struggling to edit to get server online [RenegadePkz]
channel.description: I have been editing RenegadePkz for a couple weeks so far and have tried [shadow=black,left]many attempts[/shadow] to get the server online and tried editing the server.java, client.java, and many other methods. I have all necessary programs: No-IP (registered) and uTorrent (opened port 43594 from there). My No-IP is knightscape.no-ip.biz and I replace it with the original host but no progress...
